84
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,040
Little bunny,

85
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,800
I wish you peace
and joy,

86
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:30,280
and that you will
meet your true love.

87
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:05,840
