113
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:08,320
whose conduct and ability are excellent,

114
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:10,200
either could serve as Metropolitan Governor.

115
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:16,320
The Censor’s wife is Ming Qiuhao’s cousin.

116
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:19,200
The Vice Minister of Rites is unrelated

117
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:22,120
but He Zhiqiu studied under his master.

118
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,040
I instead recommend

119
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:32,360
Hanlin Academician Liu Zhi as Governor.

120
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:36,840
Liu Zhi

121
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:42,320
tried several cases the Left Minister backed.

122
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:44,000
Replying to Your Majesty,

123
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,400
that is correct.

124
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:47,760
Where is Liu Zhi?

125
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:01,360
Fourth‑rank Hanlin Academician Liu Zhi

126
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:03,560
greets Your Majesty.

127
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,360
You judged that case quite well.

128
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:07,440
In that case,

129
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:09,760
you shall be Metropolitan Governor.

130
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,960
Report to your post tomorrow.

131
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:13,640
I

132
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,800
obey Your Majesty’s decree.

133
00:10:17,600 --> 00:10:19,320
For Capital Guard Commander,

134
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:22,560
I recommend Vice Minister Wei Ming.

135
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:24,240
Though Wei Ming serves in the Ministry,

136
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:26,760
he is not versed in military affairs.

137
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:30,480
The capital region is too critical.

138
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:31,880
General Nan,

139
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,000
you shall assume this command.

140
00:10:36,520 --> 00:10:37,080
I

141
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,520
am already advanced in years,

142
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,280
I fear I cannot manage it.

143
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,840
General Nan is in his prime

144
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,800
and can bear this commander’s post.

145
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:50,280
I

146
00:10:50,640 --> 00:10:51,960
accept the decree.

147
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:08,880
This time you dragged me onto your ship.

148
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:11,520
Yet once the edict was issued,

149
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,440
I instead felt full of drive.

150
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:15,560
Lord Liu,

151
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:17,520
you should have felt so long ago.

152
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,880
Lord Rui is right about that.

153
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:23,560
General Nan,

154
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:28,400
His Majesty meant me for Guard Commander.

155
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,680
Why did you not warn me earlier?

156
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:32,680
I also only learned

157
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:34,320
in court today.

158
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,240
But this is a good thing.

159
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:38,240
With Father in an important post,

160
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,920
others won’t trouble him so easily.

161
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,960
I only fear you’ll be targeted

162
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,720
and dragged into trouble for him.

163
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:47,400
If soldiers come, the general blocks.

164
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:48,640
If floods come, earth dams them.

165
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,960
We’ll counter each move as it comes.

166
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:54,760
Let’s go.

167
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:04,640
I wish to appoint the worthy

168
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:06,640
from the new generation of officials

169
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:08,600
to mend the civil‑military rift

170
00:12:08,880 --> 00:12:10,080
and thereby advance the Military Exam.

171
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:11,560
Lord Rui,

172
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:14,200
there is one thing I still doubt.

173
00:12:15,800 --> 00:12:18,040
You are the Left Minister’s disciple,

174
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,160
and deeply favored by the Emperor.

175
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,200
Why

176
00:12:23,280 --> 00:12:24,840
would you choose to support me?

177
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,720
Because you are upright

178
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,840
and have no bias against generals,

179
00:12:29,280 --> 00:12:29,840
and

180
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,480
you never join factional strife.

181
00:12:31,760 --> 00:12:33,360
What the court lacks most today

182
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:35,000
is forthright officials like you.

183
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:38,040
Your name truly suits your nature.

184
00:12:51,680 --> 00:12:53,000
The time has come.

185
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,480
Enter the hall.

186
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,480
You all sit for this exam today

187
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:21,240
for the sake of your future,

188
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:22,400
and for Ling An’s future.

189
00:13:23,040 --> 00:13:25,120
Whether you pass the list or not,

190
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:26,640
hold rites and law in your hearts,

191
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,200
revere the Emperor’s grace,

192
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:29,840
and you will see it through.

193
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:31,640
Announce the topic.

194
00:13:39,400 --> 00:13:41,160
Today’s palace examination topic is:

195
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:43,800
“The way to secure the nation’s army.”

196
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,400
Your Highness, please.

197
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:48,160
Prime Minister Ming.

198
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,160
Please, Minister Ming.

199
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:07,600
is the way to secure a mighty army.

200
00:14:08,800 --> 00:14:09,880
This is what Rui Yu is doing.

201
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:12,120
He wants to start with the exams

202
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:14,160
to push for the Military Imperial Exam,

203
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:16,200
cultivating new forces for himself.

204
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:19,840
Well?

205
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,960
Your Highness, even now

206
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,720
you still want to win Rui Yu over?

207
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,080
Minister Ming,

208
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,800
how could I be so short‑sighted?

209
00:14:29,640 --> 00:14:30,040
Come.

210
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:31,520
To get this done,

211
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,520
you’ll need both money and men.

212
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:35,760
Your Highness should care more about it.

213
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:36,360
Yes.

214
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,280
I still have matters to attend to.

215
00:14:40,160 --> 00:14:41,280
I shall take my leave first.

216
00:14:43,480 --> 00:14:44,400
Minister Ming, take care.

217
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:48,200
This Ming Qiuhao

218
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:50,000
is actually so rude to Your Highness.

219
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:52,040
He is the chancellor of a strong state;

220
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:55,280
why would he value a mere hostage prince?

221
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:57,480
In fact,

222
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:00,440
if Your Highness truly fancies Lord Rui,

223
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:01,960
why not expose her true identity?

224
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,480
Then you two could—

225
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:07,240
That would only make her hate me more.

226
00:15:08,800 --> 00:15:10,040
It would also harm the greater cause.

227
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:17,680
Only once I become Prince Qian Yuan

228
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:20,080
can I marry her without wronging her.

229
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:22,120
Elder Brother,

230
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:41,080
any boat crossing this river,

231
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:47,640
I’ll cut it in two without mercy.

232
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:11,240
Charge!

233
00:17:05,840 --> 00:17:06,480
Pass down the order:

234
00:17:06,840 --> 00:17:07,960
the King of Da Yue is dead.

235
00:17:08,120 --> 00:17:10,360
All who surrender to Wu Rong

236
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:11,560
shall be treated with favor.

237
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:36,360
Young Master Beicheng,

238
00:17:36,800 --> 00:17:37,880
why not stay here

239
00:17:38,120 --> 00:17:40,800
and conquer these grasslands with me?

240
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:47,320
Father,

241
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,120
Lady Ming is here as well.

242
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:55,480
Your Highness.

243
00:17:56,040 --> 00:17:56,760
You may go.

244
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:58,720
I have matters to discuss with him.

245
00:17:59,320 --> 00:17:59,800
Yes.

246
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:01,200
Your son will take his leave.

247
00:18:03,760 --> 00:18:04,560
Please, sit.

248
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:07,640
You were so eager to see me,

249
00:18:07,840 --> 00:18:08,800
what is this about?

250
00:18:11,480 --> 00:18:13,280
My men sent word to me:

251
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:15,040
this time the scripts’ review

252
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:17,400
was done solely by Rui Yu.

253
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:20,680
And my own protégés?

254
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:24,600
Only three even made the list.

255
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:29,480
Given Lord Rui’s way of doing things,

256
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:30,960
this is also within

257
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:32,160
what one would expect.

258
00:18:32,440 --> 00:18:33,680
These three men,

259
00:18:33,800 --> 00:18:35,680
I can place them in key posts.

260
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:37,040
But the top three

261
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:39,240
are all from humble families.

262
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:42,200
Rui Yu is chief examiner of this Spring Exam,

263
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:43,600
so these three men

264
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:46,760
are effectively his protégés.

265
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:52,520
No vested interest can threaten them.

266
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:55,240
So, Lord Ming,

267
00:18:55,960 --> 00:18:57,120
what do you intend to do?

268
00:18:59,080 --> 00:19:00,000
Kill them.

269
00:19:02,120 --> 00:19:03,320
As for who ranks first,

270
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,560
the Emperor will decide.

271
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:07,440
But

272
00:19:09,760 --> 00:19:11,600
it can’t be anyone but these three.

273
00:19:17,560 --> 00:19:19,560
Killing them before the exam ends,

274
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:21,200
such a big move—

275
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:22,800
I fear my men will be exposed.

276
00:19:23,120 --> 00:19:23,680
Minister Ming,

277
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:26,080
it must be done before results are posted.

278
00:19:28,520 --> 00:19:29,800
Once these three are dead,

279
00:19:30,120 --> 00:19:31,000
the vacant spots are filled,

280
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:33,560
and Rui Yu alone won’t decide it.

281
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:35,320
Of course,

282
00:19:36,160 --> 00:19:37,720
to leave no loose ends,

283
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:39,840
we must rely on Your Highness’s skill.

284
00:19:41,240 --> 00:19:41,920
Minister Ming,

285
00:19:42,760 --> 00:19:44,440
if we startle the snake in the grass,

286
00:19:44,560 --> 00:19:46,240
we’ll suffer heavy losses too.

287
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:48,720
So please think twice, Minister.

